# My API

Defines a group, which includes 'Message' section. These sections can be used to describe non-HTTP interaction.
A message may have a title and may not.

# Data Structures

## ChatMessage
+ id: 1 (number, required)
+ author
  + id: 42 (number, required)
  + name: `John Smith` (string, required)
+ text: `Hello there` (string, required)

# Group WS /chat_messages

## Message ServerToClientMessage NewParticipant
Notification about a new user being added to the channel
+ Attributes
    + name: John (string, required) - user name

## Message
+ Attributes (ChatMessage)
